{"tid":485601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"臉皮超厚！失戀男徵女陪玩北海道「晚上擠同張床」被網友嗆爆：你是沒朋友？","createTime":"2017-12-01T05:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-01T05:52:13.000Z","uid":5020,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6b176b849437b07d35550b9fe1ffbe910d6c7e9d","tid":485601,"uid":5020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:46:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://ck101.com/thread-4254964-1-1.html?ref=subj-cont-01\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fck101.com%2Fthread-4254964-1-1.html%3Fref%3Dsubj-cont-01&d=EsbRmfGEyIqgtGSc2fR%2BhwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=a403c5f6\" target=\"_blank\">https://ck101.com/thread-4254964-1-1.html?ref=subj-cont-01</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然廢宅沒有去過北海道，不過聽說北海道雪景很美呀～<br />\n最近香港連登討論區就出現一篇男網友<span style=\"color: orange;\">「徵求旅伴」</span>的貼文！<br />\n<br />\n這位男網友表示自己剛和前女友分手沒多久<br />\n希望能找到一名女性和他<span style=\"color: maroon;\">＂全家人＂</span>一起去北海道旅遊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">引來許多網友狂批是沒有其他親戚朋友嗎？</span></span> <img src=\"https://ck101.com/static/image/smiley/default/emo_002.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fck101.com%2Fstatic%2Fimage%2Fsmiley%2Fdefault%2Femo_002.gif&h=0700312b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n28日這名男網友就以<span style=\"color: maroon;\">「想請位絲打去北海道」</span>為標題徵求旅伴<br />\n希望找到年齡大約20-25歲，長相順眼就好有禮貌的女網友<br />\n與他一同和全家人進行家族旅行日期為12月13日-20日～～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaaD2TA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FaaaaaD2TA.jpg&h=f9d5f47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（圖片翻攝自／網路）</span><br />\n<br />\n他還備註說原本是要和前女友一起前往的&hellip;<br />\n但突然分手所以女網友不需要支付機酒費用<br />\n當然免費的機加酒看似很棒沒錯，卻有個 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">超 瞎 條 件</span></span> ！！！<br />\n<br />\n那就是要和男網友<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「擠在同張床上睡覺」</span></span>因為入住的飯店是一廳三房的家庭房型<br />\n雖然他表明自己什麼都不會做，更表示自己今年24歲，身高178公分（感覺就很可疑啊）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaaD2UJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FaaaaaD2UJ.jpg&h=b3c4fc6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（圖片翻攝自／網路）</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">有網友看到就直接開嗆說：「你是沒有其他親戚朋友？」、「臉皮不會太厚嗎？」<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaaD2T9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FaaaaaD2T9.jpg&h=86607e5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（圖片翻攝自／網路）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但是這名男網友看完網友留言也沒有惱羞成怒或是生氣&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n只是說沒找到女網友去也沒關係，還對前女友喊話說<span style=\"color: maroon;\">「如果妳不想虧本的話，你知道怎麼找到我的！」</span><br />\n網友看了又補他一槍分手後馬上徵求女網友一塊旅行，證明前任甩你一點也沒錯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">網友看了也爆笑留言：</span><br />\n<br />\n「會被甩還真有點道理！」<br />\n<br />\n「柴犬界林志玲說牠願意考慮&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaaD2Uz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FaaaaaD2Uz.jpg&h=3609af17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片翻攝自／網路）<br />\n<br />\n「這位小公主要報名 問你要怎麼登記」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s1.imgs.cc/img/aaaaaD2U5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs1.imgs.cc%2Fimg%2FaaaaaD2U5.jpg&h=c6b47f56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（圖片翻攝自／網路）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">廢宅：看完只覺得活該會被甩啦！！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://ck101.com/static/image/smiley/default/emo_073.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fck101.com%2Fstatic%2Fimage%2Fsmiley%2Fdefault%2Femo_073.gif&h=afcb5c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nlihkg 原post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/482255/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/482255/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n其他相關報導:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/31827?t=%E5%A4%B1%E6%88%80%E7%94%B7%E5%BE%B5%E5%A5%B3%E9%99%AA%E7%8E%A9%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%93%E3%80%8C%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A%E6%93%A0%E5%90%8C%E5%BC%B5%E5%BA%8A%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E7%B6%B2%E5%97%86%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%A0%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%EF%BC%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fdalemon%2Fpost%2F31827%3Ft%3D%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%2588%2580%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%2599%25AA%25E7%258E%25A9%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%2581%2593%25E3%2580%258C%25E6%2599%259A%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%2593%25A0%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E5%25BA%258A%25E3%2580%258D%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%2597%2586%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%258B%25E5%258F%258B%25EF%25BC%259F&d=EsbRmfGEyIqgtGSc2fR%2BhwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=2bf91242\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/dalemon/post/31827?t=%E5%A4%B1%E6%88%80%E7%94%B7%E5%BE%B5%E5%A5%B3%E9%99%AA%E7%8E%A9%E5%8C%97%E6%B5%B7%E9%81%93%E3%80%8C%E6%99%9A%E4%B8%8A%E6%93%A0%E5%90%8C%E5%BC%B5%E5%BA%8A%E3%80%8D%E3%80%80%E7%B6%B2%E5%97%86%EF%BC%9A%E4%BD%A0%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%EF%BC%9F</a>"},{"pid":"29b5dabe60731d80c9143851dab727b7f0fbaf7a","tid":485601,"uid":72193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-01T05:52:13.000Z","msg":"柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}